Game - Class in it.polimi.ingsw
Game contains all the metods that implements the match Implemented methods allows to do the following operation: addPlayer add a new player to the match moveStudentsToHall move the students from the Entrance to the hall of the dashboard setupGame start a new game checkPlayer check that there is the correct number of players to start a new match or print that the game is waiting new players
